148
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:11,830
The outside world is very exciting.

149
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:14,630
You shouldn't limit yourself
to this small place.

150
00:08:15,190 --> 00:08:17,510
Though this mansion
occupies a large area,

151
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:19,360
you should go out more

152
