to broaden your horizons.

153
00:08:35,080 --> 00:08:35,920
Sister,

154
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:37,790
did I say something wrong?

155
00:08:40,270 --> 00:08:41,110
It's fine.

156
00:08:41,390 --> 00:08:42,320
I'll head back first.

157
00:08:50,750 --> 00:08:52,670
(I didn't expect her
to be so considerate.)

158
00:08:56,480 --> 00:08:57,550
I overlooked that.

159
00:08:58,870 --> 00:08:59,910
Not your fualt.

160
00:09:00,510 --> 00:09:01,840
It's my own decision.

161
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:05,000
Just get along with Qianyu.

162
00:09:05,510 --> 00:09:07,440
Don't let me fail the late princess.

163
00:09:09,550 --> 00:09:10,390
Sure.

